==Description== <!--T:2-->

<!--T:3-->
The {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_AlignTop.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_AlignTop|Spreadsheet AlignTop]]}} tool makes the text inside the cell align to the top of the cell.

==Usage== <!--T:4-->

<!--T:5-->
# Make sure there is an active {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_CreateSheet.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_CreateSheet|Spreadsheet]]}} open so that the button is enabled.
# Select a cell.
# Press the {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_AlignTop.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_AlignTop|Spreadsheet AlignTop]]}} button.

